1. *Ovakav* problem ne može se rešiti preko noći. (Such a problem cannot be solved overnight.) 
2. Rešenje za *ovakvo* stanje je da se obrati pažnja na sve detalje. (The solution for this situation is to pay attention to every detail.)
3. Oni su imali *ovakvu* situaciju već nekoliko puta. (They have had such a situation several times.)
4. Ona je uvek imala *ovakve* misli. (She has always had such thoughts.)
5. *Ovakva* stvar se nikada ne sme zaboraviti. (Such a thing must never be forgotten.)